title: Dobbs helps Vols rally for 38-31 victory over No. 19 Georgia
text:
> Georgia Dobbs helps Vols rally for 38-31 victory over No. 19 Georgia Tennessee quarterback Joshua Dobbs (11) tries to avoid being tackled by Georgia defensive lineman John Atkins (97) and cornerback Devin Gillespie (36) during the first half of an NCAA college football game Saturday, Oct. 10, 2015, in Knoxville, Tenn.
